{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 nvk_LOOPMAKER Creates perfect zero-crossing loops out of selected items. If Loop Count is set to a number higher than 1, it will create multiple loops out of a single item that can be played back to back with sample accurate transitions.\par}
}

